name: Game & Print Club Print #13: Mushroom World Invasion
description:
Game & Print Series.

Print #13

Pre-Requisite: You must meet at least 1 of the following 3 requirements:

A. Own at least 1 game in the Super Mario RPG series (Super Mario RPG, Paper Mario series, Mario & Luigi series). 

*During the PayPal check out process, in the area under your shipping address, labelled "Note to Seller," include a link to your a photo of the game(s) and make sure somewhere in your photo your paypal e-mail is written down and visible as well.

B. Own a Wii U console. **

**Write down your Nintendo Network ID during the PayPal check out process, in the area located under your shipping address. The area is labelled as "Note to Seller."

C. Own a 3DS handheld.***

***Write down your 3DS Friend Code during the PayPal check out process, in the area located under your shipping address. The area is labelled as "Note to Seller."

(If you've provided proof via option B or C before you do not need to do it again.)

On-Sale Period: 11/21/2013 from 12 AM Pacific - 11/24/2013 at 11:59 PM Pacific.
